Ancient mez is in fact unresistable.  It works wonders when
fighting mobs like Fellspine or Phinny.

The other thing it's great for is for pvp.  Ancient mez can mez
players lvl 65.  Apparently the lvl restriction is only on npcs.
So this means that a bard with this song should never really
lose a duel....


