Lvl 55 is so that you can go to Plane of Storms and do the
quest to get flagged for Bastion of Thunder.

BoT is definitely one of the nicer zones in the game.  Most
camps give great xp, and there's a lot of nice loot to be had.

When you zone in you'll walk across 2 rooms and get to what
they call the &quot;safe room&quot;.  This is where you wait LFG.
Once you have a group, you walk out of safe room up a set of
stairs which will bring you into the 4-way.  This is a big open
area with an ...</td>
